{"type": "article", "id": 49509, "title": "农夫山泉推出狗年限定瓶，杜蕾斯调侃《旅行青蛙》 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-01-23T04:19:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 47266, "name": "狗年"}, {"id": 47267, "name": "旅行青蛙"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 26, "praise_count": 102, "image": "img/article/article_show/201801231211584t7Efq2M1hnbOagY.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"https://fashionista.com/2018/01/kardashian-jenner-family-calvin-klein-campaign\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>CK 找卡戴珊姐妹团拍了广告</b></a>，视频中五个人玩起了“从来没做过……”的游戏，挺符合她们真人秀偶像的晒私生活人设。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123120012njo5JA7Eyk1i8zWH.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712644\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25443.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>郑恺、欧阳娜娜等五位明星给 adidas neo 拍了支非常动感的广告片</b></a>，主题是：你越好（hào）玩，时尚就越好（hǎo）玩。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=r05379ughkg&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 20.0px 0.0px; line-height: 28.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 26.0px Times; color: #b31714; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 32.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 14.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 14.0px Arial; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 16.0px 'Hiragino Sans GB'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25417.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>继 2016 年金猴瓶、2017年金鸡瓶后</b></a>，农夫山泉推出的第三款限量生肖纪念版。这组金狗瓶将限量发售 24 万套，共有 5 家顶尖设计工作室参与设计。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123115411K3jd6QOJku8TncXz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.475714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=30&amp;v=RTKLahQ-e1w\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>耐克的第一支冬奥会广告上线</b></a>，依然开启排比句文案模式。广告中出现的是首个代表非洲角逐雪橇项目的尼日利亚女运动员 Seun Adigun。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123120444OzDhFEyxUWQkIstG.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.555952\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.newnownext.com/gus-kenworthy-head-shoulders-commercial/01/2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>宝洁签约美国首位公开出柜后参加冬奥会的运动员 Gus Kenworthy</b></a>，他是一名 26 岁的自由滑雪选手。在海飞丝最新的广告中 Gus 挥舞着彩虹旗说：“我的肩上扛着国家的荣誉，也扛着同志社群的骄傲。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123120253la7pUIV2bGmqwYA9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.308750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://weibo.com/durexinchina?refer_flag=1001030101_&amp;is_hot=1#1516680428781\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>杜蕾斯赶了下手游《旅行青蛙》的热点</b></a>，在官方微博上发布了一张合成的游戏截图，调侃：<a target=\"_blank\" render=\"ext\" suda-uatrack=\"key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic\" extra-data=\"type=topic\" href=\"https://huati.weibo.com/k/%E6%97%85%E8%A1%8C%E9%9D%92%E8%9B%99?from=501\" rel=\"nofollow\">#旅行青蛙#</a> <a target=\"_blank\" render=\"ext\" suda-uatrack=\"key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic\" extra-data=\"type=topic\" href=\"https://huati.weibo.com/k/%E6%97%85%E3%81%8B%E3%81%88%E3%82%8B?from=501\" rel=\"nofollow\">#旅かえる#</a>一直在计划，从未出过门。 ​​​​</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180123120903OYJsdmn7Q0aBIiMx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.778261\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><b><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25441.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pt 铂金上线了一支温馨的微电影</a>，</b>故事情节和大多数珠宝首饰广告别无二致，但一些细节上的处理，比如女主角比男主角略高半个头的设定，让短片有了记忆点。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=y0537z7th75&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><b><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/25447.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">支付宝发布一支微电影</a></b>，从主人公小男孩的角度出发，讲述了自己的抠门妈妈一系列生活琐事。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=h0536s7q1r9&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\">题图来源：农夫山泉</p>"}